Directory structure:
- 3rdParty: third party libraries that XULWin depends on
- Samples: a collection of sample XULWin applications
- Scripts: a few build scripts (internal use)
- Test: the XULWin testsuite
- xulrunnersamples: a collection of small XULRunner applications used by the testsuite
- XULWin: the XULWin library
- README: this file
- Test_vs90.sln: the Visual Studio solution for the Test project
- Tutorial_01.ln: the Visual Studio solution for the Samples/Tutorial_01 project
- Tutorial_02.sln: the Visual Studio solution for the Samples/Tutorial_02 project
- XULViewer_vs90.sln: the Visual Studio solution for the Samples/XULViewer project

